    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 40-43.</p><p>Archdruid’s Resilience</p><p>When you reach 24th level, you become resistant to cold and fire damage, both in your true form and in your Wild Shape. Additionally, whenever you finish a long rest, choose one other damage type among the following: acid, lightning, or thunder. You become resistant to that damage type in all your forms until you choose another type upon finishing a long rest.</p></div>",
